{
  "texts": [
    "Compared to VOSviewer, Bibexcel and SciMAT have very basic visualisation capabilities.",
    "A few proprietary software like HistCite offer more advanced information metric analyses but were not chosen due to accessibility reasons for the wider research community.",
    "Among freely available bibliometric software, VOSviewer provides a balance between analysis depth and ease of use (Van Eck and Waltman, 2021).",
    "Based on these technical capabilities aligned with the analytical objectives of this study, VOSviewer was selected.",
    "showing collaboration patterns between countries, organisations and authors."
  ]
}